TEXT.S: tatama, salengacay ku banges, nalecuhan i 3 a bulad 17 a demiad, 1959 a mihcan. u miunduay. Danny Ainge unu syubay kanas-mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, u mikilac zikuzay mimaliay. Danny Ainge i 1981 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 2 ku uwac atu silsil 31, namapili' tu nu Boston Celtics putiput.
